data.description: Welcome to your new home in a vibrant +55 community, fully renovated & move-in ready! This charming residence boasts 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. Gather with friends & family in the spacious living room, or delight in cooking meals in the beautiful modern-style kitchen. Revel in the luxury of brand-new flooring throughout the entire home, complemented by the stunning updates in the bathrooms. With accordion shutters in place, you'll have peace of mind during hurricane season.    Indulge in the retired lifestyle you've been dreaming of, knowing that lawn care, exterior paint, & roof maintenance are all included in the HOA fees. Speaking of which, the HOA fee is a total of $326, encompassing a $96 recreation/land lease fee. Welcome to your new home in a vibrant +55 community, fully renovated & move-in ready!
